{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"So I thought, \"I will talk about death.\""},{"time":2000,"text":"Seemed to be the passion today."},{"time":4000,"text":"Actually, it's not about death."},{"time":6000,"text":"It's inevitable, terrible, but really what I want to talk about is,"},{"time":9000,"text":"I'm just fascinated by the legacy people leave when they die."},{"time":12000,"text":"That's what I want to talk about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14000,"text":"So Art Buchwald left his legacy of humor with a video"},{"time":18000,"text":"that appeared soon after he died, saying,"},{"time":20000,"text":"\"Hi! I'm Art Buchwald, and I just died.\""},{"time":24000,"text":"And Mike, who I met at Galapagos, a trip which I won at TED,"},{"time":29000,"text":"is leaving notes on cyberspace where he is chronicling"},{"time":33000,"text":"his journey through cancer."},{"time":36000,"text":"And my father left me a legacy of his handwriting"},{"time":40000,"text":"through letters and a notebook."},{"time":42000,"text":"In the last two years of his life, when he was sick,"},{"time":46000,"text":"he filled a notebook with his thoughts about me."},{"time":50000,"text":"He wrote about my strengths, weaknesses,"},{"time":53000,"text":"and gentle suggestions for improvement,"},{"time":57000,"text":"quoting specific incidents, and held a mirror to my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":63000,"text":"After he died, I realized that no one writes to me anymore."},{"time":68000,"text":"Handwriting is a disappearing art."},{"time":71000,"text":"I'm all for email and thinking while typing,"},{"time":74000,"text":"but why give up old habits for new?"},{"time":77000,"text":"Why can't we have letter writing and email exchange in our lives?"},{"time":81000,"text":"There are times when I want to trade all those years"},{"time":87000,"text":"that I was too busy to sit with my dad and chat with him,"},{"time":91000,"text":"and trade all those years for one hug."},{"time":97000,"text":"But too late."},{"time":99000,"text":"But that's when I take out his letters and I read them,"},{"time":105000,"text":"and the paper that touched his hand is in mine,"},{"time":108000,"text":"and I feel connected to him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111000,"text":"So maybe we all need to leave our children"},{"time":115000,"text":"with a value legacy, and not a financial one."},{"time":118000,"text":"A value for things with a personal touch --"},{"time":121000,"text":"an autographed book, a soul-searching letter."},{"time":125000,"text":"If a fraction of this powerful TED audience"},{"time":128000,"text":"could be inspired to buy a beautiful paper --"},{"time":130000,"text":"John, it'll be a recycled one -- and write a beautiful letter"},{"time":135000,"text":"to someone they love, we actually may start a revolution"},{"time":138000,"text":"where our children may go to penmanship classes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141000,"text":"So what do I plan to leave for my son?"},{"time":145000,"text":"I collect autographed books, and those of you authors"},{"time":147000,"text":"in the audience know I hound you for them --"},{"time":150000,"text":"and CDs too, Tracy."},{"time":152000,"text":"I plan to publish my own notebook."},{"time":156000,"text":"As I witnessed my father's body being swallowed by fire,"},{"time":160000,"text":"I sat by his funeral pyre and wrote."},{"time":164000,"text":"I have no idea how I'm going to do it,"},{"time":165000,"text":"but I am committed to compiling his thoughts and mine"},{"time":168000,"text":"into a book, and leave that published book for my son."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172000,"text":"I'd like to end with a few verses of what I wrote"},{"time":174000,"text":"at my father's cremation."},{"time":176000,"text":"And those linguists, please pardon the grammar,"},{"time":179000,"text":"because I've not looked at it in the last 10 years."},{"time":181000,"text":"I took it out for the first time to come here."},{"time":184000,"text":"\"Picture in a frame, ashes in a bottle,"},{"time":188000,"text":"boundless energy confined in the bottle,"},{"time":191000,"text":"forcing me to deal with reality,"},{"time":194000,"text":"forcing me to deal with being grown up."},{"time":197000,"text":"I hear you and I know that you would want me to be strong,"},{"time":201000,"text":"but right now, I am being sucked down, surrounded"},{"time":205000,"text":"and suffocated by these raging emotional waters,"},{"time":208000,"text":"craving to cleanse my soul, trying to emerge"},{"time":211000,"text":"on a firm footing one more time, to keep on fighting and flourishing"},{"time":217000,"text":"just as you taught me."},{"time":219000,"text":"Your encouraging whispers in my whirlpool of despair,"},{"time":223000,"text":"holding me and heaving me to shores of sanity,"},{"time":228000,"text":"to live again and to love again.\""},{"time":230000,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}